data.description: Here is a great 1080 +/- sq/ft fixer upper that has a nearly new roof, new windows, doors, recently installed laminate flooring, a new sewer line and a new water line with 3 frost free hydrants.  Currently there is one bedroom and one full bathroom. With the addition of a closet this could easily be a 2 bedroom home.  Sweat equity would pay off at this price! The home also sits diagonally across the street from a very nice city park and pool.  This property will have to be purchased with cash or an unconventional loan due to the unfinished condition. Call today!
